					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Oh, right: BIT PPUSTATUS in the wait for vblank function. I forgot about that.<br /><br />Does anybody know of any other possible conceivable situation where the stuff can somehow misalign, even if I always read or write PPUADDR and PPUSCROLL in pairs?</div>

					
